903514%26refsrc%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.google.com%252F%26_rdr&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=afef41d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1093609467325407&amp;id=617828444903514&amp;refsrc=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2F&amp;_rdr</a><br />\n<br />\n93年講到2019 講到口臭班藍絲都仲係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895cdea4289b9b5f80936bc95a6e8f9f70f779a7","tid":1331614,"uid":278570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:32:28.000Z","msg":"約定大家721 airdrop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71bce546e346063fd3ba321c5c47b134b0cb268f","tid":1331614,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:33:19.000Z","msg":"好明顯冇<br />\n三分鐘熱度<br />\n好失望"},{"pid":"4bfe299ae84352931949ef2d26a98d71404f7eb7","tid":1331614,"uid":283449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:33:01.000Z","msg":"聽日加油，俾多 d 人知道要以行動抵制 TVB 🔥🔥🔥"},{"pid":"06f819775d2fcf7da6d0a5ac3bb46e75778839c5","tid":1331614,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:26:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1445022cd165b96e652b2f270e287ecb47fac1b","tid":1331614,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4189085a39301638f3fa38f165a26e7ef813f25b","tid":1331614,"uid":235711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:17:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c1c400d37a09ae6cdda40630760ef8c2d1bee6d5","tid":1331614,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6RKGAC8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6RKGAC8.jpg&h=11b13de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n眾籌網頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%e5%91%bd%e9%81%8b%e8%87%aa%e9%81%b8%e9%81%99%e6%8e%a7%e5%99%a8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25e5%2591%25bd%25e9%2581%258b%25e8%2587%25aa%25e9%2581%25b8%25e9%2581%2599%25e6%258e%25a7%25e5%2599%25a8%2F&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=dfdbcd2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%e5%91%bd%e9%81%8b%e8%87%aa%e9%81%b8%e9%81%99%e6%8e%a7%e5%99%a8/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XsPOZ4S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXsPOZ4S.jpg&h=395bb566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTVB報導偏頗，不盡不實，屢次抹黑反送中示威活動，出賣香港市民。<br />\n在此呼籲全港18區抗爭者，合力將所有酒樓，茶餐廳，醫院，護老院，健身室等公共空間的電視轉台。<br />\n<br />\n由TVB 81/82/83/84/85 轉去 港台 31/32，開電視 77 或 Viu TV 99台。<br />\n<br />\n原post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1320101/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1320101/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟對萬用遙控略有認識，在過去一個月，與工廠開發了一款抗爭專用遙控器 (universal remote)。<br />\n<br />\n產品可控制9大電視品牌 + 1個自選品牌，於出廠時已預設轉台及其他基本功能。 簡易操作如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 查看電視品牌<br />\n<br />\n2. 按鍵選擇該品牌<br />\n<br />\n3. 按CH+-鍵轉台<br />\n<br />\n現眾籌HKD120000，當中已包括開發和測試費用，4000件大貨，4%眾籌平台手續費，運輸到全港18區和18區智能櫃費用。<br />\n<br />\n如眾籌達標，將隨即下訂單，預計約30天內交貨。<br />\n<br />\n當貨到香港，將以捐款者提供的聯絡方式，告知所屬地區的取貨密碼和地址。<br />\n<br />\n這次眾籌屬個人自發，沒有人手，故只能用honour system，煩請捐$50者自取一件，$100者自取兩件，如此類推。 由於智能櫃有時間限制，請於通知發出後40小時內取貨。 由於無法控制參與者是否全部自律，恕不能保證捐款者一定能取得產品，只能做到盡量安排，先到先得。<br />\n<br />\n眾籌目的，不像Kickstarter或Indiegogo買產品，而是要令更多的香港抗爭者加入全港轉台行列。<br />\n<br />\n多謝支持！！ 香港人加油！！"}]}